# ── All env vars are optional ─────────────────────────────────────
# Default SQLite DB at ./blog.db, no config needed.
# To override DB path (e.g. persistent volume on Cloudflare/Render):
#   DATABASE_URL=/data/blog.db
#
# Sessions are server-side (DB-backed), no JWT secret to manage.
#
# Optional first-run bootstrap guard. When set, the setup screen requires this
# value before it can create the first admin account.
#   ADMIN_SETUP_TOKEN=replace-with-a-long-random-token
